node.text:
Happy Friday #FitFam 💪🏼
I will be live April 19th @ 7:45pm for a home body workout.
Wanna join?
💥 Download @onthego_fit FIT APP (link in bio) and sign up for my live class; you can also view and select 1:1 training session dates!
We are all in this together —let’s keep grinding! ☑️
🎥 @lee_lhgfx @alexcurson
